(1, 'Hydration: Drink plenty of water to keep your skin hydrated from the inside out.\r\n', 'Hydration is key for maintaining healthy skin. Drinking an adequate amount of water helps to keep the skin hydrated, which in turn can improve its elasticity, texture, and overall appearance. Water plays a vital role in various bodily functions, including flushing out toxins and delivering nutrients to the skin cells.', '', 'AcneRosacea.jpeg');

